OL,3,CJunior doctors reject pay offer saying
OL,4,Cstrike still on
OL,6,FThe BMA says the current pay offer
OL,7,Ffrom Health Minister Robin Swann to
OL,8,Favert strike action by junior doctors
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland is "not enough".
OL,11,FMr Swann wrote a letter this week
OL,12,Fpleading with junior doctors in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland not to strike next
OL,14,Fmonth, warning that the walkout would
OL,15,Fimpact heavily on patients.
OL,17,FThe minister said he intends to
OL,18,Fincrease junior doctors' pay by up to
OL,19,F10.7% and said that is the very limit
OL,20,Fof what can be afforded at this point.
