OL,3,CJunior doctors reject pay offer saying
OL,4,Cstrike still on
OL,6,F"We have responded to the minister's
OL,7,Fletter," said Dr Fiona Griffin, BMA NI
OL,8,Fjunior doctors committee chair.
OL,10,F"The current 'offer' is the DDRB's
OL,11,Fmost recent recommendation.
OL,13,F"We have been consistently clear we
OL,14,Fare seeking an above inflation pay
OL,15,Frise for all junior doctors and a
OL,16,Fcommitment to working with us towards
OL,17,Ffull pay restoration.
OL,19,F"As it stands, what has been offered
OL,20,Fis not enough to avert strike action
OL,21,Fand our plans for this continue.
