OL,6,F"We remain willing to work with the
OL,7,Fminister to agree an offer we believe
OL,8,Fis worth putting to our members."
OL,10,FIt follows Monday's announcement that .
OL,12,FThey are calling for an immediate,
OL,13,Fabove inflation pay award and a
OL,14,Fcommitment to full pay restoration to
OL,15,F2008 levels.
OL,17,FIn his letter, Robin Swann said: "I
OL,18,Ffully understand and sympathise with
OL,19,Fthe frustration of junior doctors over
OL,20,Fboth pay and the relentless pressure
OL,21,Fon services.
