OL,6,F"My plea is that this frustration
OL,7,Fshould not spill into industrial
OL,8,Faction that cannot achieve anything of
OL,9,Fsubstance."
OL,11,FThe letter added: "Pay erosion has
OL,12,Fbeen a consequence of UK Government
OL,13,Ffiscal policies over the past decade
OL,14,Fand has been experienced across the UK
OL,15,Fpublic sector. This is a national
OL,16,Fissue.
OL,18,F"I am committed to doing all I can to
OL,19,Fmatch awards given in England ` but
OL,20,Fparity plus for pay awards is not
OL,21,Fdeliverable."
